sources.title: Self Storage (Full Movie) Horror, Mystery
sources.description:
In this twisted tale of survival, a night watchman throws a party at a tightly-secured storage facility, but the good times turn bad when party-goers start disappearing one-by-one. As the body count rises and the blood starts to flow, the survivors must outsmart a mastermind whose horrifying plan is unfolding behind closed doors.

Directed by Tom Denucci
2013
Starring  Michael Berryman, Eric Roberts, Jonathan Silverman
